OL,3,CWar hero and 'huge character' Tommy
OL,4,CClough dies aged 93
OL,6,FGloucestershire war hero Tommy Clough
OL,7,Fhas died in hospital at the age of 93.
OL,9,FThe war veteran, who was registered
OL,10,Fblind, lived alone in Staverton in
OL,11,FGloucestershire. He died on Saturday
OL,12,F19 October in hospital.
OL,14,FTommy fought in the Korean War in 1951
OL,15,Fand spent more than two years as a
OL,16,Fprisoner of war.
