OL,3,CWar hero and 'huge character' Tommy
OL,4,CClough dies aged 93
OL,6,FHe was punished for trying to escape
OL,7,Fthe Chinese prisoner of war camp, and
OL,8,Fwas kept in what he described as "the
OL,9,Fkennel club - a wooden cage about four
OL,10,Ffeet high that was not big enough to
OL,11,Flie down in".
OL,13,FTommy was one of the last survivors of
OL,14,Fthe Battle of Imjin River in Korea -
OL,15,Fin 1951 - in which he saw active
OL,16,Fservice as a gunner, attached to the
OL,17,F1st Battalion of the Gloucestershire
OL,18,FRegiment.
