OL,3,CWar hero and 'huge character' Tommy
OL,4,CClough dies aged 93
OL,6,FThe veteran gained national attention
OL,7,Fwhen spending his 90th birthday alone
OL,8,Fduring the pandemic, receiving
OL,9,Fhundreds of birthday cards from around
OL,10,Fthe world.
OL,12,FThe Soldiers of Gloucestershire Museum
OL,13,Fpaid tribute to him on Facebook,
OL,14,Fsaying: "With heavy hearts we must
OL,15,Ftoday announce the passing of a truly
OL,16,Flegendary figure.
OL,18,F"A huge character, war hero and good
OL,19,Ffriend. Tommy Clough.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
