OL,3,CWar hero and 'huge character' Tommy
OL,4,CClough dies aged 93
OL,6,F"From here Tommy was captured by the
OL,7,FChinese and held prisoner by the North
OL,8,FKoreans for nearly three years.
OL,10,F"Upon his return to Britain, Tommy
OL,11,Fsettled in Gloucester and became a
OL,12,Frecruiter for the army. He married and
OL,13,Fhad three daughters who of course have
OL,14,Four greatest sympathies.
OL,16,F"Tommy's larger than life character
OL,17,Fwill be sorely missed by many and the
OL,18,Fworld is a darker place without him in
OL,19,Fit. RIP Sir."
